No. 10-5309. Rudy Stanko, Petitioner v. Ricardo Rios, Warden, et al. 562 U.S. 806, 131 S. Ct. 279,

178 L. Ed. 2d 8,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7824. October 4, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Eighth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 366 Fed. Appx. 725.
